    p Many parents face the dilemma over whether to raise their children in the countryside or city, but we think Bristol offers the best of both worlds, and it’s clear to see why our fair city topped #[a(href='https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/bristol-best-places-to-live-2017-9fkfg7p8f') The Sunday Times Best Place to Live Guide 2017]!
    p Here’s why growing up in Brizzle is gert lush!
    
